### Start a 3-second task (Success case)
GET http://localhost:5000/long-running?duration=3

### Start a 10-second task (Test Cancellation)
# Click "Send Request" and then immediately click "Cancel Request" in the VS Code HTTP response pane.
# Check the application console logs to see the "Work was cancelled by the client" message.
GET http://localhost:5000/long-running?duration=10

### Call Remote Endpoint (HttpClient)
# This calls httpbin.org/delay/5. Cancel this request to see HttpClient cancellation in action.
GET http://localhost:5000/remote-fetch
